{"id":266,"date":"2024-02-15T07:47:01","date_gmt":"2024-02-15T07:47:01","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/ieeeismar.org\/?page_id=266"},"modified":"2024-03-06T21:08:04","modified_gmt":"2024-03-06T21:08:04","slug":"submission-guidelines","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/ieeeismar.org\/submission-guidelines\/","title":{"rendered":"Submission Guidelines for ISMAR Journal and Conference Papers"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Please note for ISMAR 2024 both the <strong>Journal Paper Track<\/strong> and the <strong>Conference Paper Track <\/strong>partially run in parallel.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Please note that for both Journal Papers submitted to the Journal Paper Track and for Conference Papers submitted to the Conference Paper Track there are <strong>BOTH<\/strong> abstract submission deadlines and full papers submission deadlines. See the call for papers for specific dates: <a href=\"https:\/\/ieeeismar.org\/cfp\/\">https:\/\/ieeeismar.org\/cfp\/<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>All submissions must be done electronically via <a href=\"https:\/\/new.precisionconference.com\/ismar\">PCS<\/a>. Note that the use of a teaser image in papers is encouraged.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-accent-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-3e93246d07e75384afd0c309610eceb2\"><strong>Abstract Deadline<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Prior to the respective track abstract deadline, authors are required to provide:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>The paper title<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Complete abstract<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Authors<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>If the abstract form is not completed at this time with the information detailed above, then a full paper will not be allowed to be submitted.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-accent-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-183750cba9ed3bbcc8ae63cbda90ffeb\"><strong>The Full Paper deadline<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Prior to the respective track deadline, authors of submitted abstracts are required to provide:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>A complete paper submission<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Any supplementary files<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-accent-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-2af1cc8f4afd08257da7d8188f3a1344\"><strong>Paper Formatting and Page Length<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Journal Paper Track<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For the Journal Paper Track all paper submissions should be formatted using the IEEE Computer Society TVCG journal format described <a href=\"https:\/\/tc.computer.org\/vgtc\/publications\/journal\/\">here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Papers submitted to the Journal Paper Track should be 4-9 pages of text NOT including references. References should not exceed 2 pages in length. Note that the minimum length is 4 full pages of text.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Conference Paper Track<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For the Conference Paper Track all paper submissions should be formatted as ISMAR Conference Proceedings papers, using the IEEE Computer Society VGTC format described <a href=\"https:\/\/tc.computer.org\/vgtc\/publications\/conference\/\">here<\/a>.<br><br>Papers submitted to the Conference Paper Track should be 4-8 pages of text, NOT including references. References should not exceed 2 pages in length. Note that the minimum length is 4 full pages of text.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Do not hesitate to contact us for any further information.<\/em><br><em>ISMAR 2024 Programme Chairs: program_chairs@ieeeismar.org<\/em><br><em>Ulrich Eck, Misha Sra, Jeanine Stefanucci, Maki Sugimoto, Markus Tatzgern, Ian Williams<br>ISMAR 2024 Science and Technology Program Chairs<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Please note for ISMAR 2024 both the Journal Paper Track and the Conference Paper Track partially run in parallel. Please note that for both Journal Papers submitted to the Journal Paper Track and for Conference Papers submitted to the Conference Paper Track there are BOTH abstract submission deadlines and full [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"page-templates\/template-fullwidth.php","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-266","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/ieeeismar.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/266","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/ieeeismar.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/ieeeismar.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/ieeeismar.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/ieeeismar.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=266"}],"version-history":[{"count":14,"href":"https:\/\/ieeeismar.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/266\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":320,"href":"https:\/\/ieeeismar.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/266\/revisions\/320"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/ieeeismar.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=266"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}